{"id": "ChIJfYerrnPDwoARB-H2YDbT7NM", "rating": 4.1, "userRatingCount": 581, "displayName": {"text": "Residence Inn by Marriott Los Angeles Pasadena/Old Town", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Modern apartments in a casual property offering an outdoor pool, plus free breakfast & happy hours.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJfYerrnPDwoARB-H2YDbT7NM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wMWVIUnlSREpZV1hkclEwZFZlRXd0YjFZMFVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I stay in hotels 150 nights a year. This hotel is hands down the best one I've stayed in this year. A joy to stay in for 11 nights for work. Worked, rested and the service was top drawer and seamless. Peaceful , quiet huge room, excellent location in beautiful and quaint old town Pasadena everything is 5 mins walk away. Beautiful view of the church and mountains from my room! Thank you to Sarah Yamada and the entire staff that make it so great!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I stay in hotels 150 nights a year. This hotel is hands down the best one I've stayed in this year. A joy to stay in for 11 nights for work. Worked, rested and the service was top drawer and seamless. Peaceful , quiet huge room, excellent location in beautiful and quaint old town Pasadena everything is 5 mins walk away. Beautiful view of the church and mountains from my room! Thank you to Sarah Yamada and the entire staff that make it so great!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jorge McIver Arranz", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103575466532071127919/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbFNWjd9mTXojVVtazarz1P8DlCinYkxVIszKbf0sG-FKbCOU3oQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-19T03:46:21.331285530Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wMWVIUnlSREpZV1hkclEwZFZlRXd0YjFZMFVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wMWVIUnlSREpZV1hkclEwZFZlRXd0YjFZMFVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c373aeab877d:0xd3ecd33660f6e107"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfYerrnPDwoARB-H2YDbT7NM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKSFpqQlJXbXh1VTJaSk5UVk5hWGhJUVZOUFVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Very good location near Colorado Old Town\nBut WARNING. 2 years ago we complained about Room 517. The HVAC system (likely the cold air return) vibrates and emits a low frequency rumble. It’s really bad at night. We complained then and moved rooms. But. omg RI NEVER BOTHERED to fix the problem. We stayed again just last weekend and got stuck in Room 517 again. Nothing changed in the last 2 years. Still vibrating ALL NIGHT LONG. Earplugs are no help.  So we had to move rooms again. I commented and told the hotel via chat and in person.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very good location near Colorado Old Town\nBut WARNING. 2 years ago we complained about Room 517. The HVAC system (likely the cold air return) vibrates and emits a low frequency rumble. It’s really bad at night. We complained then and moved rooms. But. omg RI NEVER BOTHERED to fix the problem. We stayed again just last weekend and got stuck in Room 517 again. Nothing changed in the last 2 years. Still vibrating ALL NIGHT LONG. Earplugs are no help.  So we had to move rooms again. I commented and told the hotel via chat and in person.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "C Noma", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111341600184266965146/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-BcgTIltHCWg42HiQnNBmTrCXQL9zraeoLwCrEcqu9LsTNtdc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-17T20:54:19.856338748Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKSFpqQlJXbXh1VTJaSk5UVk5hWGhJUVZOUFVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKSFpqQlJXbXh1VTJaSk5UVk5hWGhJUVZOUFVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c373aeab877d:0xd3ecd33660f6e107"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfYerrnPDwoARB-H2YDbT7NM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WWWRVZHFUWEpUTTFwcldtVlpOMEp1YjJrNFMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I stayed in the Residence Inn with my parents during the month of November last year. My experience was great! The rooms were nicely sized, and management was very responsive. I was especially grateful to Ricky who provided excellent customer service and made our three week stay a delight.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I stayed in the Residence Inn with my parents during the month of November last year. My experience was great! The rooms were nicely sized, and management was very responsive. I was especially grateful to Ricky who provided excellent customer service and made our three week stay a delight.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Salma Z", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117787520908916994339/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOerJgd3uxLJ4LsrpJu040FzyivKjBnWo2bZGKmT9pjqjL6nY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-02T23:39:02.536666337Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WWWRVZHFUWEpUTTFwcldtVlpOMEp1YjJrNFMwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WWWRVZHFUWEpUTTFwcldtVlpOMEp1YjJrNFMwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c373aeab877d:0xd3ecd33660f6e107"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfYerrnPDwoARB-H2YDbT7NM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wdVdFVnRRa3A0YVRCMWVrbDZSRTl1TWtOSFMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We loved staying here for P